{"ID":"20260415112123-0jzqelg","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260415112123-0jzqelg","title":"数字逻辑学习重排草稿","type":"doc","updated":"20260424150639"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260415114623-xklmshh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-xklmshh","updated":"20260415114623"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"好，这次我按"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"这本《夏宇闻数字逻辑设计》原书结构"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"来重做，但​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"不完全照目录顺序硬讲"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，而是按你的实际情况重新排：你会 C，其他基础还可以，但​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"时序逻辑弱、testbench 弱"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，所以教学重点要从“语法背诵”改成“时序思维 + 可综合写法 + 仿真验证”三条主线。原书本身就是从概念、设计方法、基本语法、抽象层次、运算逻辑、控制逻辑、状态机、RISC CPU 实例，再到进阶练习来展开的。"}]},{"ID":"20260415114623-70np1xk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-70np1xk","updated":"20260415114623"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"重新设计后的教学总纲"}]},{"ID":"20260415114623-nbpgjze","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-nbpgjze","updated":"20260415114623"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第一阶段：建立 Verilog 的整体脑图"}]},{"ID":"20260415114623-gin15tl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-gin15tl","updated":"20260415114623"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"目标：先知道自己到底在学什么，避免一上来陷进语法细节。"}]},{"ID":"20260415114623-4tlg072","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-4tlg072","updated":"20260415114623"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260415114623-lgzlxp9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-lgzlxp9","updated":"20260415114623"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260415114623-cg25i2q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-cg25i2q","updated":"20260415114623"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Verilog 到底是干什么的\n讲“算法 → 电路 → FPGA/ASIC”的关系"}]}]},{"ID":"20260415114623-ubim4j7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-ubim4j7","updated":"20260415114623"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260415114623-6wkh0hn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-6wkh0hn","updated":"20260415114623"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Top-Down 设计思想\n为什么要先分模块、再逐层实现"}]}]},{"ID":"20260415114623-ycgidhj","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-ycgidhj","updated":"20260415114623"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260415114623-46o9cp6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-46o9cp6","updated":"20260415114623"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"模块、端口、层次调用的整体概念"}]}]},{"ID":"20260415114623-4usuyny","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-4usuyny","updated":"20260415114623"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260415114623-jxqssv5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-jxqssv5","updated":"20260415114623"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"仿真、综合、布局布线分别是什么"}]}]},{"ID":"20260415114623-d86svai","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-d86svai","updated":"20260415114623"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260415114623-d18ht11","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-d18ht11","updated":"20260415114623"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C 语言思维和 Verilog 思维的区别"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260415114623-a2vhkib","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-a2vhkib","updated":"20260415114623"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这一阶段主要对应原书第 1、2 章，因为书里先讲算法/硬线逻辑基本概念，再讲 HDL、Top-Down、层次管理和设计流程。"}]},{"ID":"20260415114623-hamalku","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20260415114623-hamalku","updated":"20260415114623"}},{"ID":"2026041511462